column2: SELECT pl.plate, pl.mjd, sp.fiberID, ph.modelMag_u, ph.modelMag_g,   ph.modelMag_r, ph.modelMag_i, ph.modelMag_z, ph.ra, ph.dec, sp.z, ph.ObjID FROM   photoObj ph, specObj sp, plateX pl WHERE sp.bestObjid = ph.ObjID  AND pl.plateID = sp.plateID  AND sp.zWarning = #  AND sp.z BETWEEN # AND #
